{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onerror\"><code>onerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>ongotpointercapture</code></a></li><li><em><code>onload</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadeddata\"><code>onloadeddata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadedmetadata\"><code>onloadedmetadata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadend\"><code>onloadend</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadstart\"><code>onloadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture\"><code>onlostpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onpause\"><code>onpause</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplay\"><code>onplay</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplaying\"><code>onplaying</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>onload</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a> ミックスインのプロパティで、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a>、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a> 要素などで発生した <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\" title=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/load\">load</a></code> イベントを処理する<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Events/Event_handlers\">イベントハンドラー</a>です。</p>\n\n<p><code>load</code> イベントは指定されたリソースの読み込みが完了したときに発行されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> functionRef<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>functionRef</code> は、ウィンドウの <code>load</code> イベントが発行されたときに呼び出されるハンドラー関数です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">doSomethingElse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>onload test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    // ES5\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load イベントが検出されました。\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    // ES2015\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">load</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load イベントが検出されました。\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>load イベントは、文書の読み込みが完了したときに発行されます。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"メモ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>load</code> イベントは文書の読み込み工程の終了時に発行されます。このイベントが発行された時点で、文書中のすべてのオブジェクトが DOM 内にあり、すべての画像、スクリプト、サブフレームの読み込みが完了しています。</p>\n\n<p><code>DOMContentLoaded</code> や <code>DOMFrameContentLoaded</code> のような <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Events\">DOM イベント</a> (<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a> で扱うことが可能) もありますが、これらはこのページの DOM が構築された後、他のリソースの読み込みが完了する前に発行されます。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-onload","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onload"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onload","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\" title=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/load\">load</a></code> イベント</li>\n  <li><code>DOMContentLoaded</code> イベント (<a href=\"/ja/docs/Listening_to_events_in_Firefox_extensions#Simple_DOM_events\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">イベントの待ち受け: 単純な DOM イベント</a>内)</li>\n  <li>IIFE <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Immediately-invoked_function_expression\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external\">Immediately-invoked function expression</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"メモ","id":"notes"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"onload は GlobalEventHandlers ミックスインのプロパティで、Window、XMLHttpRequest、<img> 要素などで発生した load イベントを処理するイベントハンドラーです。","popularity":0.0009,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}